							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
							      d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 text-center">Programmable Thermostats</h3>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-4">
						These thermostats allow you to set temperature schedules for different times of the day and days of the
						week. By automatically adjusting temperatures when you're away or asleep, programmable thermostats help
						reduce energy consumption while maintaining comfort when you need it.
					</p>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-4">
						Programmable thermostats are an excellent entry-level option for homeowners looking to improve energy
						efficiency without the higher cost of smart thermostats. They're reliable, easy to use, and can still
						provide significant energy savings compared to manual thermostats.
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Smart Thermostats -->
				<div class="bg-lightgray p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
					<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
