						     stroke="currentColor">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
							      d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 text-center">Smart Thermostats</h3>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-4">
						Smart thermostats take programmable features to the next level by learning your preferences and habits over
						time. These advanced devices can automatically create and adjust schedules based on your behavior, optimize
						settings for energy efficiency, and provide detailed energy usage reports.
					</p>
					<p class="text-darkgray mb-4">
						Many smart thermostats also offer features like occupancy sensing, which detects when you're home or away,
						and adaptive recovery, which intelligently preheats or precools your home to reach your desired temperature
						exactly when scheduled, maximizing both comfort and efficiency.
					</p>
				</div>

